strings: <voice_0x010018F5><se_def>Dhoulmagus: How many years has it been now...? How many years spent scrubbing floors and dusting shelves...? Is this truly what it is to be a sage's apprentice?
<voice_0x010018F6><se_def>Dhoulmagus: He hasn't taught me a thing. What little magic I do know, I've had to teach myself...if such piffling parlour tricks can even be called magic.
